---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Innov-8 — ExaCap Portfolio" description="Innov-8: Panel management platform for field service operations across energy, utilities, and financial services.">
  <section class="bg-white dark:bg-accent-800 py-24 sm:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <a href="/#portfolio" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-primary-500 hover:text-primary-600 font-medium mb-8">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
        Back to Portfolio
      </a>

      <div class="flex items-center gap-6 mb-8">
        <img src="/logos/innov8.png" alt="Innov-8" class="h-14 w-auto block dark:hidden" />
        <img src="/logos/innov8-light.png" alt="Innov-8" class="h-14 w-auto hidden dark:block" />
        <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/30 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-green-700 dark:text-green-400">Active</span>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-secondary-500 dark:text-white">Innov-8</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-secondary-400 dark:text-gray-300">
        A single platform to manage all field service operations &mdash; consolidating agency relationships, automating case allocation, and providing real-time performance tracking.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        {['Field Services', 'Utilities', 'Energy', 'Financial Services', 'Panel Management', 'B2B SaaS'].map(tag => (
          <span class="inline-flex rounded-md bg-gray-100 dark:bg-accent-600 px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-secondary-400 dark:text-gray-400">{tag}</span>
        ))}
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-secondary-500 dark:text-white">Overview</h2>
        <p class="text-secondary-400 dark:text-gray-300">
          Innov-8 addresses a &pound;500m+ industry handling over 7 million annual field visits across the UK. The platform replaces fragmented spreadsheets, emails, and manual processes with a unified system that sits between client organisations and their network of field service agencies.
        </p>
        <p class="text-secondary-400 dark:text-gray-300">
          Energy suppliers, water retailers, banks, lenders, and local authorities use Innov-8 to manage site visit requirements, track agency performance in 12-week cycles, and deploy resources based on postcode-level data analysis. The platform delivers up to 50% improvement in customer engagement through optimised allocation, with AI-powered quality assurance and complete audit trails.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-secondary-500 dark:text-white mt-10">How ExaCap Helps</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-secondary-400 dark:text-gray-300">
          <li>Founding partner &mdash; ExaCap involved from inception</li>
          <li>Full 0-1 product build: architecture, application development, and deployment</li>
          <li>Cloud infrastructure setup and production-ready scaffolding</li>
          <li>Ongoing engineering support and fractional CTO guidance</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-secondary-500 dark:text-white mt-10">Key Metrics</h2>
        <div class="not-prose grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-6">
          <div class="rounded-xl bg-secondary-50 dark:bg-accent-700 p-6 text-center">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-500">10%</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-secondary-400 dark:text-gray-400 mt-1">ExaCap Ownership</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl bg-secondary-50 dark:bg-accent-700 p-6 text-center">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-500">Active</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-secondary-400 dark:text-gray-400 mt-1">Status</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl bg-secondary-50 dark:bg-accent-700 p-6 text-center">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-500">Founding</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-secondary-400 dark:text-gray-400 mt-1">Partnership Type</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
